<meta name="description" content="Cambridge Waterproofing - Gold Coast Waterproofing provides specialist systems and solutions to waterproofing requirements in both the residential &amp; commercial property markets in Australia (Brisbane, Queensland, Canberra, Sydney). With a track record of success in both small &amp; large projects, Cambridge Waterproofing is well placed to meet your exact sealant requirements. You may contact our QLD office for more details about waterproofing products and installation. Our success is based on the following key project management criteria: Sourcing competitively priced materials for all stages of the project. Performing works in locations where minimal or no disruption to the property’s tenants is imperative. Management of an experienced team with particular focus on consistency of output, adherence to quality assurance procedures &amp; consistently meeting completion dates. Extensive liaison with you the customer, including regular reporting on project status &amp; inspection at critical stages."/>
